title: Vault Reserve Price
body:
This proposal is to increase the buyout price of our fractional vault.

Recently, we added 4 Bored Apes to our vault for a total cost of 128 ETH. These apes are now worth > 200 ETH in total.

We are proposing to increase the buyout (reserve) price in order to reflect the addition of these apes and increase in value of our other purchases.

Proposal Choices:

1 - Increase to 1500 ETH
2 - Increase to 2000 ETH
3 - Increase to 2500 ETH
4 - Leave the same

P.S Current vault price of competing DAOs is around 1500 ETH
author: 0x6F76CD7F9B06c27045AD4a9FEb376b65164BfeC3
